{"ts":"2026-07-11T16:07:09.068Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-1mwk"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-513: pm next ready[] documented as ranked but not priority-ordered; no rank/score exposed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"GH-513 (dogfood, pm 2026.7.11): pm next --help promises 'ranked ready and blocked queues' and recommended is correctly priority-first, but ready[] order matches neither priority nor creation nor updated_at (repro: p1/p3/p2), and rows carry order:null, reasons:null, no score/rank key — JSON consumers cannot trust or reconstruct the ranking. Fleet impact compounds GH-509/pm-fjxm: after recommended is claimed, agents fall back to ready[0], so straightforward iteration picks lower-priority work. Preferred fix (issue option 1, least surprise): sort ready[] with the same comparator that selects recommended so ready is a true continuation; optionally also expose rank/reasons per row (option 2). Duplicate check: registry + pm search (ready queue ranked/rank score) — pm-g543 is unknown-command suggester ranking, pm-4k6b is the relevance-engine ADR territory, PR#502 pm-next defects all closed; no overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","cli","gh-issue","multi-agent"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-11T16:07:09.068Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-11T16:07:09.068Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"ready[] in pm next --json is ordered by the exact comparator used to pick recommended (priority-first plus existing tie-breakers) with a regression spec covering the GH-513 repro (p0 recommended, ready strictly p1,p2,p3); help text and docs match actual behavior; decision recorded whether per-row rank/reasons are exposed; GH-513 closed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"61b641178e02b609b78fd902d6a939019930fa27721974b58e91ffb0e14fa021","message":""}
